# CODEOWNERS — branch-protection complement.
#
# The content lane (src/content/**) is unowned: the OpenLegion engine opens
# PRs there and they auto-merge on green CI. Everything that defines the
# quality gate, the routing, or the SEO surface IS owned — those PRs require
# explicit human review so the engine cannot silently weaken the gate that
# governs its own output.
#
# Replace @openlegion-ai/maintainers with the actual GitHub team handle.

